                <div class="tit_nav">
                    <span class="tit_l">您所在位置：</span><a href="/Home/Index">首页</a><b>></b><span>案例信息</span>
                </div>
                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5904" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">CSR-0095</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8897 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">红了日子、绿了青山：民营企业永钢的环境担当</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">A Beautiful Countryside and Well-off Dwellers: Environmental Responsibility of Private Enterprise YongGang</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘文玲，杜琛仪，易瑾超，桑晶，魏一鸣</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京理工大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江苏永钢集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">民营企业；绿色转型；环境社会责任；共建共享；2021百优案例；精准扶贫与企业社会责任专项</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Private Enterprise；Green Transformation; Environmental Social Responsibility；Building and Sharing Together</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">钢铁行业作为碳排放大户，一直面临着巨大的节能减排压力。近年来，去产能、供给侧改革、“双碳”目标等一系列政策约束不断督促着钢铁企业的绿色转型，民营钢铁企业的生存和发展更显得步履维艰。起源于村办企业的永钢集团却在时代和行业阵痛中探索出一条可持续发展的环境友好道路，建设了山青水绿的“花园式工厂”，与共生的永联村携手构建了共同富裕的现代化新农村。本案例通过回顾永钢在发展过程中的几次关键改革决策，再现了永钢如何从一个名不见经传的小企业发展成行业绿色转型和新农村建设的典范。对本案例的讨论和学习可以帮助学生了解企业发展中存在的利益相关关系，分析企业为何以及如何践行企业环境社会责任，并理解环境社会责任在推动企业可持续发展中的作用。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As a major carbon emitter, the steel industry has been facing enormous pressure to reduce energy consumption and emissions. In recent years, a series of policy constraints such as capacity reduction, supply-side reform and &quot;double carbon&quot; targets have been urging steel companies to make a green transformation, making the survival and development of private steel companies even more difficult. In the midst of the pains in the times and the industry, YongGang Group has explored a sustainable and environmentally friendly way to build a &quot;garden-style factory&quot; with green hills and water, and a modern and prosperous new village with a symbiotic YongLian village. By reviewing several key transformation decisions made by YongGang in the course of its development, this case redisplays how YongGang developed from a small and unknown enterprise into a model of green transformation and new rural construction. The discussion and study of this case study will help students understand the stakeholder relationships that exist in business development, analyze why and how companies practice CSR, and understand the role of CSR in promoting sustainable business development.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《商业伦理》、《企业社会责任》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">利益相关者理论；环境压力-状态-响应；企业环境社会责任&amp;企业环境行为；企业社会责任理论及其驱动因素；战略性企业社会责任；企业绿色发展驱动力机制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-01</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5904" target="_blank">点击查看</a></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看案例使用说明</th>
